{"tid":1291241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懇請明天大家一定要揸緊「五大訴求」！","createTime":"2019-07-06T19:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T05:26:50.000Z","uid":90601,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b679ce4af14544d05b284a706ffc38beebaa962","tid":1291241,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:22:34.000Z","msg":"聽日好可能會有老黑，藍絲同警鬼搞事<br />\n甚至可能同自由行蝗蟲有衝突<br />\n去到鳩鐵站仲可能有黑警唔舉旗就出手挑釁<br />\n但係制度上而言，包括黑警在內，依班人都只係爛頭卒<br />\n今次遊行係和理非回合，最緊要令更多人了解到五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</code></pre>"},{"pid":"cbc90e8d9007c433e91f09532b8b8bf70b1d0bed","tid":1291241,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:23:12.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"3650298edc311651aaf41b978e2a75eb6d38688b","tid":1291241,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:23:24.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"c2beaddcf49bf9c59b74cf102e3feb9919635fd4","tid":1291241,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:23:34.000Z","msg":"我要食野"},{"pid":"b28fafd5c8ba72d71feced041581eef38a038148","tid":1291241,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:23:49.000Z","msg":"我有權唔解鎖"},{"pid":"0e3e99e8d28ecd37c56e6cc89016e2da03e13ec0","tid":1291241,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:23:59.000Z","msg":"唔好兇我　我投訴你"},{"pid":"3a32b112d01f9fdf26fc7753ed722abe723285eb","tid":1291241,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:28:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11076fa1e22a373dd9de41b625360818c9ea18c6","tid":1291241,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T19:38:28.000Z","msg":"我都係無野講"},{"pid":"57fa63809419e9915c719c814a58219cf1d63958","tid":1291241,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:25:51.